{"word":"G35 - ἀγενεαλόγητος - agenealógētos - ag-en-eh-al-og'-ay-tos - Without descent","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀγενεαλόγητος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">agenealógētos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ag-en-eh-al-og'-ay-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Without descent</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"வம்ச வரலாறு இல்லாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"of whose descent there is no account without genealogy"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G1075 - γενεαλογέω - genealogéō - ghen-eh-al-og-eh'-o/1075\">G1075</a>; <i>unregistered</i> as to birth: - without descent.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1074/1074\">G1074</a>, <a href=\"#/G1075/1075\">G1075</a>, <a href=\"#/G1076/1076\">G1076</a>, <a href=\"#/G35/35\">G35</a>"}]}